          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    Activation",
                "The pile-neutron capture cross section of Pu-238 was",
                "measured by inserting three quartz capsules, each",
                "containing about a microgram of the same Pu-238 used",
                "in the fission cross-section measurements, into the",
                "rabbit facility of the Materials Testing Reactor for",
                "approximately two, three, and five days' neutron",
                "irradiation, respectively.",
                "After separation and purification of the plutonium,",
                "plated samples were made, and the amount of Pu-239",
                "produced in each irradiation was determined by",
                "fission-counting."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "27-CO-59(N,G)27-CO-60,,SIG",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "27-CO-59(N,G)27-CO-60,,SIG",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "27-CO-59(N,G)27-CO-60",
                        "target": "27-CO-59",
                        "projectile": "N",
                        "process": "G",
                        "product": "27-CO-60",
                        "quantity": ",SIG",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",SIG"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The pile-neutron flux was monitored by the neutron-",
                "capture activation of cobalt wire and the results were",
                "corrected for resonance neutron activation and",
                "self-protection."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "It was necessary to make a slight correction in the",
                "fission-counting rate for those fissions contributed",
                "by Pu-238."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Allowing for the destruction of a small fraction of",
                "the Pu-238 and of Pu-239 during its formation, the",
                "resulting Pu-238/Pu-239 ratio and the known integrated",
                "neutron flux on each sample yield a capture cross",
                "                           section of 520+-40 barns."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
